@startuml seq-add-internal-contact
' Context: contacts
' Profile: client
' SDD: PROM-PERSONAL-CONTACTS-011
' Revision: 2026-07-19

title Contacts — aggiunta contatto internal (Alfred)

actor Utente
participant "UI" as UI
participant "ContactsMachine" as CM
participant "Supabase" as DB

Utente -> UI : cerca utente
UI -> CM : SearchProfiles(query)
CM -> DB : SearchProfiles
DB --> CM : ProfileSearchResults
CM --> UI : results

Utente -> UI : seleziona profilo
UI -> CM : AddInternalContact(profile)
CM -> DB : AddInternalContact
DB --> CM : ContactAdded

CM -> CM : LoadContacts
CM -> DB : LoadContacts
DB --> CM : ContactsLoaded
CM --> UI : rubrica aggiornata

@enduml
